      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Wonderful for my oily skin",
          "reviewText": "I\u2019ve been using this powder foundation for years after looking for an alternative to high end liquid foundation. My reason was mostly to cut down time on doing my makeup and something lightweight but covers decently and doesn\u2019t add to my oily skin issue. This compact is perfect. 220 is the perfect shade for my light neutral Asian skin. It lasts through the work day with blotting my face throughout (skin\u2019s too oily for any makeup to truly stop oil production - not the products fault). It also does not break me out so long as I clean the applicator or blender sponge regularly. I like that it\u2019s convenient in a compact with a mirror. I do wish the compact had more product in it bc I can go through it kind of fast, but it\u2019s hard to find a powder foundation that has good coverage, great formula, and is relatively affordable - so I\u2019ll take it.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 26, 2026",
          "customer": "Kaaarinnn",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHE7SBNIA2NXIL4TVH3GXQA6MDQA",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
